{"tid":1737400,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Poly一個都不能少 和理非再炸爆INGO","createTime":"2019-11-19T03:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T06:56:03.000Z","uid":172882,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"23a2290cdddb42b95bde1753c89002edce499ffc","tid":1737400,"uid":172882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T03:00:37.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">請大家幫手出力炸INGO 我哋而家呢個情況必須徵求外援<br />\n有目標 有文字範本 有圖 只差人力!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">點解INGO幫到手？</span></ins></strong><br />\n因香港已經陷入人道危機 社會失序 Poly斷水斷電嘅 生命危在旦夕 絕對唔係離地嘢 好多係香港有基地嘅INGO長期將喺香港籌到嘅錢捐去做人道救援<br />\n救香港係佢哋責任!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">人道危機係乜？</span></ins></strong><br />\n根據聯合國減災風險辦公室（UNDRR），災難為「由危險事件的發生、脆弱性、應付能力的相互作用下，導致任何規模的社區或社會功能被嚴重打亂，引致以下一種或多種的情況：人類，物質，經濟和環境損失及影響」。而災難可以由自然力量如地震、但亦可以由人為事件包括戰爭、內部衝突及恐怖主義等促發。 當前危機有機會演變為災難。 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">- 即係香港 PolyU姨家面臨嘅危機</span>[/size=4][/size=4]</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">INGO點解唔做嘢？</span></ins></strong><br />\n佢哋唔可能唔知香港有事，只係唔夠壓力郁唔到手，我地齊心壓爆佢!! <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋可以點做？</span></ins></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>1⃣ 炸佢地Facebook<br />\n- 逐個Post派嬲<br />\n- 留言<br />\n- Send訊息炸inbox</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標FACEBOOK: </span></ins></strong><br />\n樂施會 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oxfamhongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foxfamhongkong%2F&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=0aa891b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oxfamhongkong/</a><br />\n樂施會國際 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Oxfam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FOxfam%2F&d=uyJPOi