/>\n無國界醫生 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/msf.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmsf.hk%2F&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=57dba14b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/msf.hk/</a><br />\n無國界醫生國際 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/msf.english/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmsf.english%2F&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfIICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=b49c7a34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/msf.english/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">文字範本（歡迎自己寫或加減）：</span></ins></strong><br />\n香港正面對前所未見的人道危機，大量小孩和平民的人權甚至生命危在旦夕，請盡 貴機構的能力去幫助他們！<br />\nHong Kong is facing a humanitarian crisis that has never been seen before. The human rights and even the lives of a large number of children and civilians are at stake. Please do your best to help them! <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 圖文並茂更搶眼：</span></ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xLQfsyk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxLQfsyk.jpg&h=78ff8c1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37f3BqV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37f3BqV.jpg&h=603a207f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9XP0DEh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9XP0DEh.jpg&h=17fca0bc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NMai9LZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNMai9LZ.jpg&h=d5f5d949&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VqpjUcG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqpjUcG.jpg&h=62afe523&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/avzv0SK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Favzv0SK.jpg&h=d14ca9cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQXEUcM.jpg\" 